snippet.title: Demons, dread beyond imaginations｜Mad World - Age of Darkness - MMORPG
snippet.description:
Mad World Official Launch on April 27th (Thur)
✨Pre-registrators: https://www.madworldmmo.com

[Field] Laws and rules have no power on Gruzaam.
[Instance Dungeon] You must arm yourself to survive. Get ready with the best materials and equipment and put yourself against cruel, gruesome challenges.
[Boss] Powerful monsters behave like gods. You must prepare yourself with meticulous strategy and extraordinary power.
[Ancient Boss] Once the abyssal sky opens, demons much more vicious than the average will land upon earth. Defeat the evil and make yourself a savior.
=====================================
We have reached 500 thousand pre-registrators!
Now let’s go for 1 million!

Pre-register now if you have not taken part in our pre-registration events yet!

✨Pre-registrators: https://www.madworldmmo.com
=====================================
